		<title>Mayo Clinic Minute: Dual procedure combines liver transplant, bariatric surgery</title>
		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-minute-dual-procedure-combines-liver-transplant-bariatric-surgery/
		
		<dc:creator><!--[CDATA[Deb Balzer]]--></dc:creator>
		<pubdate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 16:50:20 +0000</pubdate>
